《'''逆轉檢事2'''》（{{lang-ja|逆転検事2}}），是一款由[[卡普空|卡普空]]開發的[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]][[文字冒險遊戲|文字冒險遊戲]]，亦是[[逆轉裁判系列|逆轉裁判系列]]第六個遊戲和《[[逆轉檢事|逆轉檢事]]》的續作。<ref name="Announcement">{{cite web |url=http://www.andriasang.com/e/blog/2010/09/09/ace_attorney_sequel/ |title=Capcom Formally Announces Ace Attorney Investigations 2 |author=Anoop Gantayat |date=September 9, 2010 |work= |publisher=Andriasang |accessdate=September 9, 2010 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130121000021/http://andriasang.com/comp2m/ace_attorney_sequel/ |archivedate=2013-01-21 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>卡普空指出他們還沒有計劃在外國發佈此遊戲。<ref name="Capcom Forums">{{cite web|title=Why Arent You Localizing Ace Attorney Investigations 2?|url=http://www.capcom-unity.com/ask_capcom/go/thread/view/7371/27423285/Why_Arent_You_Localizing_Ace_Attorney_Investigations_2?pg=3|accessdate=10 April 2011}}</ref>本作是逆轉裁判系列中唯一一個沒有在日本國外發佈的遊戲。<ref name="Capcom Forums"/>

==遊戲系統==
[[File:GK2gameplay.png|thumb]]
本作與其前作《[[逆轉檢事|逆轉檢事]]》的遊戲系統較為相似。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2010-12-03-ace-attorney-investigations-2-details | title = Ace Attorney Investigations 2 details | first = Wesley | last = Yin-poole | date = 2010-12-03 | accessdate = 2010-12-03 | publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | archive-date = 2010-12-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101206081413/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2010-12-03-ace-attorney-investigations-2-details | dead-url = no }}</ref>
玩家在遊戲中將會扮演檢察官御劍-{怜}-侍。此遊戲主要分為兩個部分：調查及辯駁。<ref name="Announcement"/>本作新增了一個遊戲模式：邏輯象棋。當玩家與一定角色對話時，邏輯象棋就會啟動。在邏輯象棋中，玩家需要在有限的時間內找出對方的弱點，並在兩種對話選擇中挑選合適的對話來攻擊對方的弱點。若玩家取得優勢時，玩家就會得到一個象棋來摧毀對方的象棋。但若玩家處於劣包勢時，玩家的時間欄就會減少。若時間欄減少至零，遊戲就會結束。當玩家摧毀了對方所有的象棋後，玩家就完成了邏輯象棋。<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.joystiq.com/2010/09/17/ace-attorney-investigations-2-preview/ | title = Ace Attorney Investigations 2 preview: My first game of Logic Chess | first = JC | last = Fletcher | date = 2010-09-17 | accessdate = 2010-09-17 | publisher = [[Joystiq|Joystiq]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100919002407/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/09/17/ace-attorney-investigations-2-preview/ | archive-date = 2010-09-19 | dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.destructoid.com/tgs-hands-on-with-miles-edgeworth-2-184244.phtml | title = TGS: Hands on with Miles Edgeworth 2 | publisher = [[Destructoid|Destructoid]] | date = 2010-09-17 | accessdate = 2010-09-17 | archive-date = 2016-03-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160325124600/http://www.destructoid.com/tgs-hands-on-with-miles-edgeworth-2-184244.phtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>此遊戲與其他逆轉裁判系列遊戲不同，其裁判官是一位女性。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.siliconera.com/2010/09/17/edgeworths-new-rival-in-ace-attorney-investigations-2-is-a-stern-female-judge/ | title = Edgeworth’s New Rival In Ace Attorney Investigations 2 Is A Stern Female Judge | publisher = Siliconera | date = 2010-09-17 | accessdate = 2010-09-17 | archive-date = 2015-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150922093357/http://www.siliconera.com/2010/09/17/edgeworths-new-rival-in-ace-attorney-investigations-2-is-a-stern-female-judge/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

==劇情概要==
第一案件中，西鳳民國大統領王帝君來到日本葫蘆湖公園進行演講，結果在演講進行到一半時突然有暗殺者想要暗殺王帝君。經過調查後，御劍成功找出真兇，保鑣內藤馬乃介<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.1up.com/news/miles-edgeworth-rides | title = Miles Edgeworth Rides Again | first = Kevin | last = Gifford | date = 2010-09-08 | accessdate = 2010-09-08 | publisher = [[1UP.com|1UP.com]] | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121016050519/http://www.1up.com/news/miles-edgeworth-rides | archivedate = 2012-10-16 }}</ref>。

第二案件中，時間回到18年前的IS-7事件，當時的辯護律師為御劍信，嫌疑犯是天海一誠。第二天，西鳳民國大統領王帝君遭人殺害。同時，相澤詩紋遭到綁架，犯人以他的性命威脅水鏡裁判官。

第三案件“继承的逆转”发生在同一地方的两个不同时期，相差18年。在倒叙片段中，御剑怜恃的父亲御剑信跟年轻的信乐盾之，为涉嫌谋杀同行冰堂伊作的著名厨师天海一诚作辩护。

第四案件“被遗忘的逆转”一案中，身负重伤兼有失忆的一条美云来到御剑怜恃的办公室，被指控谋杀辩护律师笼目翼。

第五案件“宏大的逆转”一案在一个小时（也许不到）内发生，王帝君突然离开死亡。御剑在案发现场再次碰到狼士龙，狼由于在调查走私集团（见《[[逆转检事|逆转检事]]》）一案中处理不当，失去了100人的手下团队。

==發佈==
逆轉檢事2首次於2010年9月初在《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》上亮相，之後卡普空便正式宣佈此遊戲正在開發中。於2010年的[[东京电玩展|东京电玩展]]上，卡普空展示了本作的試玩版本。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.siliconera.com/2010/09/07/eureka-ace-attorney-investigations-2-announced/ | title = Eureka! Ace Attorney Investigations 2 Announced | author = Spensor | publisher = Siliconera | date = 2010-09-07 | accessdate = 2010-09-07 | archive-date = 2015-01-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150129224757/http://www.siliconera.com/2010/09/07/eureka-ace-attorney-investigations-2-announced/ | dead-url = yes }}</ref>

=== 本地化 ===
2011年3月，卡普空的克里斯汀·斯文森指出他們並沒有計劃製作本作的國外版本。<ref name="Capcom Forums"/><ref>[http://www.ustream.tv/recorded/13406869 Ask Capcom]</ref>於2011年12月的人一個訪問中，斯文森指出他們可能會發佈一個可下載的《逆轉檢事2》遊戲。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2011/12/09/from-resident-evil-to-asuras-wrath-capcoms-plans-for-next-year/ |title=From Resident Evil To Asura’s Wrath, Capcom’s Plans For Next Year |accessdate=2013-08-19 |archive-date=2016-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411184946/http://www.siliconera.com/2011/12/09/from-resident-evil-to-asuras-wrath-capcoms-plans-for-next-year/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2012年1月，斯文森再次指出他們仍然沒有放棄製作本作的國外版本。<ref>{{cite video|people=Christian Svensson |year=2012 |title=Devil May Cry 2 (Pt. 2) |url=http://www.twitch.tv/capcomunity/b/306354674 |format= |medium= |language=en |publisher= |location= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120207021917/http://www.twitch.tv/capcomunity/b/306354674 |archivedate=2012-02-07 |accessdate=2012-02-05 |time=4:27 |ref= |deadurl=yes }}</ref>於2012年3月，他指出他們正在討論是否製作本作的國外版本，並希望「支持者仍然有足夠的耐性」。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2012/03/13/capcom-going-big-with-resident-evil-6.aspx |title=Capcom Going Big With Resident Evil |author=Jim Reilly |date=March 13, 2012 |work=Game Informer |accessdate=March 14, 2012 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303172555/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2012/03/13/capcom-going-big-with-resident-evil-6.aspx |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

2012年8月，一位卡普空員工指出若《逆轉裁判123HD重製》是一個成功的作品，那麼卡普空便有可能製作《逆轉檢事2》的國外版本。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.capcom-unity.com/xantista/blog/2012/08/29/phoenix_wright:_ace_attorney_hd_trilogy_coming_to_iphone_and_ipad_this_fall |title=Phoenix Wright: Ace Attorney HD Trilogy coming to iPhone and iPad this Fall |author=Chris |date=August 29, 2012 |publisher=[[Capcom|Capcom]] |accessdate=September 2, 2012 |quote=Erick: "Does this increases {{sic}} the chances of a localization of AAI2?..."<br/>Chris: "It will if it's a success ;)"}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://forums.court-records.net/viewtopic.php?f=31&t=23724 |title=Carrot on a Stick |author=Wooster |date=August 30, 2012 |publisher=Court-Records |accessdate=September 2, 2012}}</ref>

2012年9月，當斯文森被問到《逆轉裁判123HD重製》的成功會否鼓動卡普空製作《逆轉檢事2》的國外版本時，他指出這兩個遊戲並沒有關係，《逆轉裁判123HD重製》的成功不會鼓動卡普空製作《逆轉檢事2》的國外版本。<ref name="sales forecasts">{{cite web |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2012/09/17/ace-attorney-5-sales-forecasts-are-aggressive-say-capcom-usa/ |title=Ace Attorney 5 Sales Forecasts Are "Aggressive" Say Capcom USA |author=Ishaan |date=September 17, 2012 |publisher=[[Siliconera|Siliconera]] |accessdate=September 18, 2012 |archive-date=2016-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411205934/http://www.siliconera.com/2012/09/17/ace-attorney-5-sales-forecasts-are-aggressive-say-capcom-usa/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2013年1月，斯文森再三被問及卡普空會否製作《逆轉檢事2》的國外版本。斯文森指出因為《[[逆轉裁判5|逆轉裁判5]]》的銷售更佳，所以他們正在製作《逆轉裁判5》的國外版本，因此沒有空閒的時間和人力資源去製作《逆轉檢事2》的國外版本。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.capcom-unity.com/ask_capcom/go/thread/view/7371/29604851/whats-going-on-with-aai2&post_num=92#528060779 |title=What's going on with AAI2? |author=Christian Svensson |date=January 14, 2013 |publisher=Capcom |accessdate=January 15, 2013}}</ref>但後來製作者江城元秀卻指出他們正在排程製作此遊戲的國外版本。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/why-ace-attorney-investigations-2-never-made-it-to-amer-512745313 |title=Why Ace Attorney Investigations 2 Never Made It To America |accessdate=2013-08-19 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304002602/http://kotaku.com/why-ace-attorney-investigations-2-never-made-it-to-amer-512745313 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==銷售==
本作在日本發佈後，成為了日本銷售量最高的遊戲之一。截至2011年2月9日，本作已於日本售出逾132,000套遊戲。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://kotaku.com/#!5756431/the-last-story-gives-up-first-for-more-legal-drama-in-japan | title = The Last Story Gives Up First For More Legal Drama In Japan | first = Michael | last = McWheator | date = 2011-02-09 | accessdate = 2011-02-09 | publisher = [[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | archive-date = 2012-02-26 | archive-url = https://www.webcitation.org/65jtEC8RX?url=http://kotaku.com/#!5756431/the-last-story-gives-up-first-for-more-legal-drama-in-japan | dead-url = no }}</ref>截至2013年8月3日，本作已於日本售出逾260,000套遊戲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vgchartz.com/game/47197/ace-attorney-investigations-2/|title=Ace Attorney Investigations 2|publisher=VGChartz|date=2013-08-03|accessdate=2013-08-19}}</ref>

